SELECT "statuses"."id" FROM "statuses" WHERE "statuses"."account_id" = $? AND "statuses"."id" <= $? AND "statuses"."deleted_at" IS ? AND (NOT EXISTS (SELECT ? FROM bookmarks bookmark WHERE bookmark.account_id = statuses.account_id AND bookmark.status_id = statuses.id)) ORDER BY "statuses"."id" ASC LIMIT $?
